subtitleNullable: Uncover the hidden manipulations in COVID-19 X-ray images
descriptionNullable:
This is a tampered dataset from the original dataset “COVID-19 Radiography Database.” [Online]. Available: https://www.kaggle.com/tawsifurrahman/covid19-radiography-database. 

CM - Copy Move Forgery Technique 
S - Splicing Forgery Technique 

This dataset consist of 9 classes and they are
{
COVID-19 2000 images
CM COVID-19 2000 images
S COVID-19 2000 images
Viral Pneumonia 1340 images
CM Viral Pneumonia 1340 images
S Viral Pneumonia 850 images
Normal 2000 images
CM Normal 2000 images
S Normal 2000 images
}

if you use this dataset, kindly, cite 
Khalifa, Nour Eldeen; abd El-Latif, eman I. (2022), “COVID-19 Digital X-rays Forgery Dataset”, Mendeley Data, V1, doi: 10.17632/3bzv6t24ts.1
